[30;1m25 | [0m[35m## Function-based middlewares[0m
[30;1m26 | [0m[35mTo use function-based middleware, you should set `apihelper.ENABLE_MIDDLEWARE = True`.[0m
[30;1m27 | [0m[35mThis type of middleware is created by using a decorator for middleware.[0m
[30;1m28 | [0m[35mWith this type middleware, you can retrieve update immediately after update came. You should set upd[0m
[30;1m29 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m30 | [0m[35m## Why class-based middlewares are better?[0m
[30;1m31 | [0m[35m- You can pass data between post, pre_process functions, and handler.[0m
